quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  47,1,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe …ďe falii laawol Allah ngol, O bonnii golle ma…ď…ďe …óen"
  47,2,"Gom…óim…ďe …ďen …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe, …ďe gom…óini ko jippinaa kon e Muhammad - on goonga immor…óo e Joomi ma…ď…ďe - O yawtanii …ďe bon…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, O mo∆ī∆īinii fiyaaku ma…ď…ďe on"
  47,3,"Ko wa…ói …óum, ko tawde yeddu…ďe …ďen jokkii meere nden, gom…óim…ďe …ďen kan jokki goonga kan immorde e Joomi ma…ď…ďe on. Ko wano nii Allah piyiranta yim…ďe …ďen mise ma…ď…ďe …óen"
  47,4,"Si on arii hawrude e yeddu…ďe …ďen (ka hare), ko soppugol daa…óe …óen. Haa si on …óu…ó…óinii warugol …ďe, ha…ď…ďon koy…óe …óen. Ko si on mo∆ī∆īoray e ma…ď…ďe accitugol …ďe …ďaawo …óum, maa si ko soktiigu, haa hare nden wallina jogaaji mayre. Ko non √Īaawiraa, si Allah no muuyunoo, O wallitotono on e ma…ď…ďe, ko woni tun, ko no O jarribora yoga mon e dow yoga. Waraa…ďe fii Allah …ďen, pellet, O yeebataa golle ma…ď…ďe …óen"
  47,5,"Arma O fewna …ďe, O mo∆ī∆īina fiyaaku ma…ď…ďe"
  47,6,"O naadoya …ďe Aljanna, mo O anndini …ďe fii mun"
  47,7,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, si on wonii walloo…ďe fii Allah, O wallay on, O tabintina teppe mon …óen"
  47,8,"Yeddu…ďe …ďee kan, halkaare woodanii …ďe, O majjinii kadi golle ma…ď…ďe …óen"
  47,9,"∆äum le ko tawde …ďe a√Īii ko Allah jippini kon, O bonni golle ma…ď…ďe …óen"
  47,10,"E …ďee yiilaaki e leydi ndin, …ďe teskoo ko honno battane adinoo…ďe …ďen wa'unoo? Allah halkuno fii ma…ď…ďe. sugu mum kadi hino woodani yeddu…ďe …ďen"
  47,11,"Ko wa…ói …óum, ko tawde ko Allah woni gi…óo gom…óim…ďe …ďen; hara non yeddu…ďe …ďen, gi…óo (woo) alanaa …ďe"
